1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:42,940
(Jingyuan Manor)

3
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,000
Your Highness,

4
00:00:48,479 --> 00:00:49,560
a report just came.

5
00:00:49,759 --> 00:00:52,159
The Prince has reached the city gate.

6
00:00:54,620 --> 00:00:58,900
(Jingyuan Manor)

7
00:00:58,940 --> 00:01:02,860
=Episode 21=

8
00:01:17,159 --> 00:01:18,280
So much for your watch.

9
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,200
Remember, speak only

10
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,120
when I tell you to.

11
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:29,079
Got it?

12
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,719
This is...

13
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:56,200
Xiaojiu.

14
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,519
How did she end up like this?

15
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,519
This is Xiaoyi?

16
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:07,159
After Wu Lian assaulted her,

17
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,960
this is what she became.

18
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:12,560
So the embroiderer at the mass
grave wasn't Xiaoyi?

19
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,080
No.

20
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,960
Ms. Meng Wan switched the bodies.

21
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,919
She saved Xiaoyi

22
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,919
and entrusted her to me.

23
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,840
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

24
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,719
Ms. Meng didn't want to
distract you.

25
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,039
She said...

26
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:25,960
What did she say?

27
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:28,560
If one day she's gone,

28
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,120
take good care of Xiaoyi.

29
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,400
Don't be afraid.

30
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:46,599
Xiaoyi,

31
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,520
look at me.

32
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,199
Do you recognize me?

33
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,800
I'm Rulan.

34
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:56,680
Xiaoyi,

35
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,800
let's take revenge together.

36
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:00,719
Will you do it?

37
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:11,159
But you must learn to speak.

38
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:13,120
Get better, you hear me?

39
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:18,520
Yes.

40
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:33,080
Wu Xin.

41
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,599
Master Wu.

42
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:40,000
Wu Xin went out and hasn't returned yet.

43
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,520
Why are you panicking?

44
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,479
It...

45
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,360
It's the Prince's return.

46
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:45,520
The steward told everyone
to gather at the inner gate.

47
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,560
I...

48
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:48,280
The Prince is back?

49
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,080
Yes.

50
00:03:57,039 --> 00:03:59,479
(First Among Princes. Mengqiu Pavilion)
Lady Cheng'en's birth chart is blessed

51
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,680
and processed through all proper rites.

52
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,280
It just needs to match the Prince's.

53
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,840
Please take a look.

54
00:04:07,940 --> 00:04:10,220
(Marriage Contract)

55
00:04:10,380 --> 00:04:12,900
(Xiao Zhengyang, Prince Jingyuan)

56
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,800
Are you pleased?

57
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,040
Where is Lady Cheng'en?

58
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:22,519
So it's clear

59
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:25,079
you returned for her.

60
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:28,040
Didn't I already come to see you?

61
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:30,920
Your beauty is as great as ever.

62
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,519
Do you really mean that?

63
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,560
The contract has been delivered.

64
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,839
Why haven't you invited her yet?

65
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:39,959
Your Highness,

66
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:43,879
your wish is to keep the Prince
in the manor

67
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,240
by your side.

68
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:49,000
Besides, Lady Cheng'en is only...

69
00:04:51,839 --> 00:04:53,639
There's no need to rush.

70
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,839
She's already in the manor.

71
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,680
You are virtuous

72
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,040
and wise.

73
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:04,920
Are you displeased?

74
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,079
If you're happy,

75
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,199
then I'm happy.

76
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,800
I was just thinking,

77
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,639
when I was young,

78
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:17,319
you always stayed by my side.

79
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,040
We've been married for over
a decade.

80
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:21,199
Why do you still say that?

81
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,519
Go and invite Lady Cheng'en again.

82
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:28,680
Yes.

83
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:33,600
The Prince has returned today.

84
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:35,000
Please be very careful.

85
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:37,399
Don't worry. We've long been prepared.

86
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:42,439
But Xiaoyi...

87
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,439
I'll take care of her.

88
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,680
You can count on me.

89
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:47,439
If anyone gives you trouble tonight,

90
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,319
don't push yourself too hard.

91
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,480
Don't worry. I know my limits.

92
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:55,279
I'll wait by the west side gate
for your word.

93
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,800
Thank you, my friends.

94
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,519
Tonight at the third watch,

95
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,480
same place.

96
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:02,000
Let's go.

97
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:11,839
Explain for your Lady.

98
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:15,439
My Lady kept changing her clothes today,
unhappy with each.

99
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:16,439
Then she said she wanted

100
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:19,920
to find garments that would please
the Prince at the market.

101
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,879
I've never seen Ruoheng so particular.

102
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,639
Now that the Prince is back...

103
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,199
Who are you talking about, Wenyue?

104
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:40,480
You. I see you every day.

105
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,920
Now that the Prince is back,

106
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,439
after so many invitations,

107
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,600
and you still don't show up.

108
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,639
I came here for you, Wenyue.

109
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,439
Don't make fun of me.

110
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,920
It's not that I don't want
to see the Prince.

111
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,319
It's just...

112
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:55,279
So you can be shy too.

113
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,160
Ruoheng,

114
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,079
greet the Prince.

115
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:04,680
Greetings, Your Highness.

116
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,399
Raise your head.

117
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,279
Why stare so eagerly?

118
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,800
There will be plenty of time later.

119
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,879
It's our first meeting.

120
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,639
I hope you'll forgive my awkwardness.

121
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:58,879
Could Ms. Meng Wan have
made a mistake?

122
00:08:21,319 --> 00:08:23,399
Wu Lian is so sinister.

123
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,440
Found it?

124
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,879
That scumbag!

125
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:19,120
A true beast.

126
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:21,440
Ten beheadings wouldn't be enough.

127
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,600
I couldn't quite believe it myself.

128
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:26,080
Someone who can create
such fine embroidery...

129
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,240
I never thought he'd stoop so low.

130
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:29,799
But...

131
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,440
This beast

132
00:09:31,759 --> 00:09:33,720
risks everything to keep this on him.

133
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:35,559
He'll take it out and savor it

134
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,480
again and again.

135
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:40,080
But he ended up weaving his
own trap.

136
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:41,919
So many embroiderers,

137
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:46,000
but only Rulan dared
to report to the authorities.

138
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:48,440
I hate my own cowardice back then.

139
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,879
Should we proceed carefully?

140
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:52,200
Exactly.

141
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,320
This involves too much,

142
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,440
too many reputations,

143
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,519
and even lives.

144
00:09:57,919 --> 00:09:59,080
We need to be careful.

145
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,039
Xiaoyi,

146
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:03,840
Xiaoyi,

147
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,080
don't be afraid.
It's just a handkerchief.

148
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:10,600
Don't be afraid.
No one will hurt you anymore.

149
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:15,879
Don't be afraid.

150
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,399
You're good now.

151
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,080
We need to tell Rulan right away

152
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,120
that we found the list.

153
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,440
I'm here.

154
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,240
Don't be afraid.

155
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,639
Don't be afraid.

156
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:03,260
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

157
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:06,500
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

158
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:10,460
♪The past no longer binds♪

159
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:14,660
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

160
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:19,220
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

161
00:11:20,060 --> 00:11:22,940
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

162
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:25,300
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

163
00:11:25,300 --> 00:11:29,380
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

164
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:31,980
♪For your faith that never broke♪

165
00:11:32,180 --> 00:11:36,300
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

166
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:39,100
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

167
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:43,340
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

168
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:47,020
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

169
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:49,780
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

170
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:52,380
♪One thought turns into ash♪

171
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:58,700
♪No future left to write♪

172
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:01,580
♪If I never fall♪

173
00:12:01,620 --> 00:12:03,980
♪How could this waiting end♪

174
00:12:03,980 --> 00:12:05,340
♪If I bear no scars♪

175
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:07,660
♪How could I challenge fate♪

176
00:12:07,660 --> 00:12:10,020
♪I knew there was no way back♪

177
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:14,020
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

178
00:12:14,140 --> 00:12:16,260
♪For your faith that never broke♪

179
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:20,420
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

180
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:23,300
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

181
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:27,700
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

182
00:12:28,780 --> 00:12:31,380
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

183
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:33,980
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

184
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:36,340
♪One thought turns into ash♪

185
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:42,700
♪No future left to write♪

186
00:12:43,580 --> 00:12:45,980
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

187
00:12:47,260 --> 00:12:49,380
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

188
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:53,260
♪If we meet again someday♪

189
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:59,500
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪

